00:28:32.431 --> 00:28:37.222
Look at this chump.
You shut the door in our faces. asshole!

265
00:28:37.306 --> 00:28:40.389
Watch what you're saying.
You weren't the only ones in danger!

266
00:28:41.722 --> 00:28:43.222
What a piece of work.

267
00:28:43.972 --> 00:28:46.930
Come here. I will throw you out.

268
00:28:47.014 --> 00:28:49.597
Stop it! Everyone's just scared.

269
00:28:54.889 --> 00:28:56.472
<i>Attention. please!</i>

270
00:28:56.555 --> 00:29:02.597
<i>Due to our current situation.
we won't be stopping in Cheonan.</i>

271
00:29:02.680 --> 00:29:06.430
<i>For your safety.
please stay in your seats.</i>

272
00:29:07.680 --> 00:29:08.847
Excuse me.

273
00:29:08.930 --> 00:29:09.930
What's going on?

274
00:29:11.555 --> 00:29:13.305
Hello? Anyone there?

275
00:29:14.138 --> 00:29:15.638
<i>Yes. go ahead!</i>

276
00:29:15.722 --> 00:29:19.638
Do you even know
what's going on back here?

277
00:29:19.721 --> 00:29:21.513
Why aren't you stopping in Cheonan?

278
00:29:21.596 --> 00:29:22.888
<i>We're aware. sir.</i>

279
00:29:22.971 --> 00:29:26.388
<i>I've just evacuated as well.
But it's an order from our control center.</i>

280
00:29:26.471 --> 00:29:27.596
<i>Please be seated.</i>

281
00:29:27.680 --> 00:29:32.346
That's nonsense! People are going rabid!

282
00:29:32.846 --> 00:29:34.805
Stop in Cheonan. got it?

283
00:29:36.513 --> 00:29:37.471
Excuse me.

284
00:29:41.554 --> 00:29:44.388
I'm really sorry.
but do you think she could sit down?

285
00:29:44.471 --> 00:29:46.013
- She's pregnant.
- Stop it.

286
00:29:46.096 --> 00:29:47.638
- Okay.
- Take a seat.

287
00:29:47.721 --> 00:29:49.638
- I'm fine.
- Thank you.

288
00:29:49.721 --> 00:29:51.054
MOM

289
00:29:52.804 --> 00:29:53.679
Mom?

290
00:29:53.762 --> 00:29:57.262
<i>Are you on your way?</i>

291
00:29:58.304 --> 00:29:59.887
Yes. we're en route.

292
00:30:00.887 --> 00:30:02.929
Where are you and why is it so loud?

293
00:30:03.012 --> 00:30:06.554
<i>What's happening? Everyone's fighting.</i>

294
00:30:07.471 --> 00:30:11.137
<i>Are you and Su-an okay?</i>

295
00:30:11.220 --> 00:30:13.637
You are breathing hard. Are you hurt?

296
00:30:15.095 --> 00:30:17.970
<i>Seok-u. my baby!</i>

297
00:30:18.054 --> 00:30:22.470
<i>Please take care of Su-an.</i>

298
00:30:23.262 --> 00:30:24.470
Mom. you okay?

299
00:30:25.762 --> 00:30:28.262
<i>My dear Su-an...</i>

300
00:30:31.720 --> 00:30:37.553
<i>I love her so much.
but she only wants her mom.</i>

301
00:30:40.303 --> 00:30:41.928
<i>You bastards!</i>

302
00:30:50.011 --> 00:30:50.970
Mom?

303
00:30:53.553 --> 00:30:54.553
Dad.

304
00:30:57.053 --> 00:30:58.136
Dad!

305
00:31:00.303 --> 00:31:02.303
Is Grandma okay?

306
00:31:10.094 --> 00:31:12.928
- What the hell?
- What is it?

307
00:31:13.678 --> 00:31:15.303
Sweetie. let's sit down.

308
00:31:29.469 --> 00:31:30.636
Open the door!

309
00:32:00.135 --> 00:32:01.843
<i>My fellow citizens.</i>

310
00:32:02.718 --> 00:32:06.968
<i>We're currently experiencing
violent riots in all major cities</i>

311
00:32:07.052 --> 00:32:09.260
<i>including seoul.</i>

312
00:32:09.343 --> 00:32:14.177
<i>resulting in many civilian
and police injuries.</i>

313
00:32:14.885 --> 00:32:19.343
<i>Riots have led
to the shutting down of various districts.</i>

314
00:32:19.426 --> 00:32:24.218
<i>and some rioters have destroyed
police buses. or climbed the roofs</i>

315
00:32:24.301 --> 00:32:26.593
{\an8}<i>in an attempt to hijack them.</i>

316
00:32:26.676 --> 00:32:28.093
{\an8}<i>Good job.</i>

317
00:32:28.801 --> 00:32:32.093
{\an8}<i>For this reason.
we're entering a state of emergency</i>

318
00:32:32.843 --> 00:32:39.009
{\an8}<i>in order to keep our citizens safe
and control the current situation.</i>

319
00:32:41.593 --> 00:32:44.843
<i>Thanks to our government's rapid response.</i>

320
00:32:44.926 --> 00:32:47.301
<i>the number of riots are decreasing.</i>

321
00:32:47.384 --> 00:32:48.218
Be quiet!

322
00:32:48.301 --> 00:32:51.676
<i>The situation will be resolved soon.</i>

323
00:32:52.884 --> 00:32:54.217
<i>Fellow citizens.</i>

324
00:32:54.842 --> 00:33:01.009
<i>please refrain
from reacting to baseless rumors</i>

325
00:33:01.092 --> 00:33:06.926
<i>and stay in the safety of your homes.</i>

326
00:33:07.009 --> 00:33:10.217
{\an8}<i>We must stay calm and trust the government</i>

327
00:33:10.300 --> 00:33:13.425
{\an8}<i>in order to overcome
such trying obstacles.</i>

328
00:33:14.509 --> 00:33:18.300
<i>We believe
that your safety is not in jeopardy.</i>

329
00:33:31.883 --> 00:33:33.342
ANALYST KIM

330
00:33:33.425 --> 00:33:35.175
CASUALTIES INCREASE
NOT JUST A PROTEST

331
00:33:40.092 --> 00:33:42.175
Mommy's phone is off.

332
00:33:46.133 --> 00:33:49.091
Those in the front. hurry up!

333
00:33:49.591 --> 00:33:50.966
Su-an. sit over here.

334
00:33:51.758 --> 00:33:54.008
Don't worry. I'll give her a call.

335
00:33:54.091 --> 00:33:55.966
My goodness.

336
00:33:56.050 --> 00:34:00.258
- Come sit over here.
- You're older. You sit down.

337
00:34:00.341 --> 00:34:01.341
I'm fine. Take it.

338
00:34:01.424 --> 00:34:02.758
Baby. let's go over there.

339
00:34:07.341 --> 00:34:10.174
Ma'am. take my seat.

340
00:34:10.258 --> 00:34:13.424
- I'm okay.
- No. please sit.

341
00:34:17.216 --> 00:34:20.132
Child. would you like one?

342
00:34:21.424 --> 00:34:22.841
Hurry and go.

343
00:34:22.924 --> 00:34:24.632
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

344
00:34:24.716 --> 00:34:26.424
What a great kid.

345
00:34:31.299 --> 00:34:33.174
- We both got seats.
- Keep walking.

346
00:34:34.424 --> 00:34:35.549
That bag...

347
00:34:37.465 --> 00:34:39.757
Su-an. you didn't have to do that.

348
00:34:40.340 --> 00:34:41.299
Do what?

349
00:34:41.799 --> 00:34:42.799
Being nice.

350
00:34:43.299 --> 00:34:45.965
At a time like this.
only watch out for yourself.

351
00:34:49.299 --> 00:34:50.215
Answer me.

352
00:34:55.465 --> 00:34:58.173
Grandma always had knee aches.

353
00:35:00.423 --> 00:35:01.257
Sweetie.

354
00:35:06.507 --> 00:35:09.757
<i>May I have your attention?
We apologize for the inconvenience.</i>

355
00:35:10.298 --> 00:35:13.756
<i>Our train will conclude
service at Daejeon station.</i>

356
00:35:14.506 --> 00:35:20.006
<i>Military is deployed there.
and will secure our train.</i>

357
00:35:20.090 --> 00:35:24.006
<i>so every passenger
must exit once we arrive.</i>

358
00:35:24.090 --> 00:35:29.006
<i>I repeat.
Daejeon station is our last stop.</i>

359
00:35:29.090 --> 00:35:31.423
Which cities can be entered?

360
00:35:31.506 --> 00:35:34.173
Yeosu. Uljin. Busan. What about Daejeon?

361
00:35:34.256 --> 00:35:36.298
Excuse me. Let me use the bathroom.

362
00:35:36.381 --> 00:35:38.173
What about Daejeon?

363
00:35:38.256 --> 00:35:39.506
Why not?

364
00:35:41.298 --> 00:35:43.881
Sweetie. stay here for a moment.

365
00:35:47.839 --> 00:35:50.047
- Hey. kiddo.
- Yes?

366
00:35:50.631 --> 00:35:52.172
Who is he? Your dad?

367
00:35:53.172 --> 00:35:54.006
Yes.

368
00:35:54.089 --> 00:35:55.672
- Real dad?
- Yes.

369
00:35:56.631 --> 00:35:58.047
It just seems strange.

370
00:35:59.047 --> 00:36:00.089
What does he do?

371
00:36:00.172 --> 00:36:02.547
He's a fund manager.

372
00:36:02.631 --> 00:36:05.130
- Fund manager?
- Yes.

373
00:36:05.797 --> 00:36:07.339
He's a bloodsucker.

374
00:36:08.589 --> 00:36:10.339
He leaches off others.

375
00:36:10.422 --> 00:36:13.630
Don't say that in front of his child.

376
00:36:13.714 --> 00:36:18.255
It's okay. That's what everyone thinks.

377
00:36:24.297 --> 00:36:25.255
Want some?

378
00:36:26.588 --> 00:36:28.088
It's what Sleepy eats.

379
00:36:29.713 --> 00:36:32.088
This is Sleepy. Say hello.

380
00:36:33.505 --> 00:36:35.922
Your baby's name is Sleepy?

381
00:36:36.005 --> 00:36:39.838
No. the fetus name. It's like a nickname.

382
00:36:39.922 --> 00:36:44.255
Her dad is too lazy
to come up with a name yet.

383
00:36:46.338 --> 00:36:48.421
- Touch her belly.
- Right here.

384
00:36:50.130 --> 00:36:51.046
Go on.

385
00:36:56.880 --> 00:36:57.713
Felt it?

386
00:36:59.504 --> 00:37:01.129
I made that.

387
00:37:05.004 --> 00:37:07.171
- You idiot.
- But it's true. no?

388
00:37:08.671 --> 00:37:09.921
LEMMINGS

389
00:37:12.671 --> 00:37:13.713
DAEJEON LT. MIN

390
00:37:20.337 --> 00:37:23.296
<i>Mr. Seo. you called me at a bad time.</i>

391
00:37:23.379 --> 00:37:24.546
Wait!

392
00:37:24.629 --> 00:37:27.379
- Let me ask you something.
<i>- What?</i>

393
00:37:29.004 --> 00:37:30.587
I'm on the KTX to Daejeon.

394
00:37:30.671 --> 00:37:35.087
<i>KTX? You mean </i>the <i>KTX?</i>

395
00:37:35.170 --> 00:37:36.337
So. you heard?

396
00:37:37.379 --> 00:37:40.587
Is it true that the military
is deployed in Daejeon?

397
00:37:41.504 --> 00:37:42.920
<i>Yes. that's correct.</i>

398
00:37:44.254 --> 00:37:47.629
Is that so? It must be safe there.

399
00:37:49.712 --> 00:37:51.837
<i>Well. it's...</i>

400
00:37:53.545 --> 00:37:56.587
Min. it's safe. right?

401
00:37:57.503 --> 00:38:01.212
<i>Once you arrive. you'll be quarantined.</i>

402
00:38:01.712 --> 00:38:03.212
<i>- I'm sorry.</i>
- What?

403
00:38:07.170 --> 00:38:09.045
I'm with my daughter.

404
00:38:10.628 --> 00:38:13.878
Can you help me and my daughter?

405
00:38:15.795 --> 00:38:19.170
- <i>But the thing is...</i>
- I'll get you a real scoop.

406
00:38:19.253 --> 00:38:20.295
Come on. please.

407
00:38:22.420 --> 00:38:26.586
<i>Don't go to the main square.
Come to the east one.</i>

408
00:38:26.669 --> 00:38:28.461
<i>I'll let my men know.</i>

409
00:38:28.544 --> 00:38:31.586
Okay. Thank you so much.

410
00:38:39.544 --> 00:38:40.711
All dead.

411
00:38:45.127 --> 00:38:46.336
All dead.

412
00:38:57.419 --> 00:38:59.252
- What's going on?
- Are they not here?

413
00:38:59.336 --> 00:39:01.127
- So quiet.
- Is this Daejeon?

414
00:39:09.085 --> 00:39:10.085
There's nobody.

415
00:39:10.835 --> 00:39:11.877
No one here?

416
00:39:29.918 --> 00:39:30.835
Excuse me.

417
00:40:21.709 --> 00:40:23.376
What's going on back there?

418
00:40:26.501 --> 00:40:30.043
This is that violent incident
I told you about.

419
00:40:30.126 --> 00:40:31.126
Conductor!

420
00:40:31.209 --> 00:40:33.043
- Conductor?
- Yes.

421
00:40:33.959 --> 00:40:38.001
How many can fit in the engine car?
We must uncouple it and go to Busan.

422
00:40:38.084 --> 00:40:38.918
- Uncouple?
- Yes!

423
00:40:39.001 --> 00:40:40.626
- We can't.
- Why not?

424
00:40:40.710 --> 00:40:42.168
We can't do it here.

425
00:40:43.751 --> 00:40:46.085
Where's the military?

426
00:40:46.168 --> 00:40:49.626
Right. I only received a report about it.

427
00:40:49.710 --> 00:40:51.460
Where's my business card?

428
00:40:52.168 --> 00:40:57.377
I'm COO of Stallion Express.
All routes into Daejeon are cut off.

429
00:40:57.460 --> 00:41:00.377
- Our buses are all rerouted.
- What do you mean?

430
00:41:00.460 --> 00:41:02.877
The city's been blockaded!

431
00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:04.835
They probably won't let us in.

432
00:41:04.919 --> 00:41:09.585
But South Shore is still open.
so let's go to Busan!

433
00:41:09.669 --> 00:41:12.210
Wait. if that's true.

434
00:41:12.294 --> 00:41:14.127
we must take others.

435
00:41:14.210 --> 00:41:15.544
- Take who?
- I mean...

436
00:41:15.627 --> 00:41:18.086
- Let's check the station first.
- Hey!

437
00:41:21.461 --> 00:41:22.294
Damn it!

438
00:41:44.920 --> 00:41:47.628
RESTRICTED AREA

439
00:42:01.379 --> 00:42:03.337
RESTRICTED

440
00:42:05.420 --> 00:42:06.712
Don't mind them.

441
00:42:13.046 --> 00:42:15.087
- Come on. sweetie.
- Where are we going?

442
00:42:16.421 --> 00:42:17.754
We're going this way.

443
00:42:17.837 --> 00:42:19.046
Just us?

444
00:42:19.629 --> 00:42:20.837
Yes. let's go.

445
00:42:27.088 --> 00:42:27.921
What is it?

446
00:42:30.421 --> 00:42:31.796
I'm going that way.

447
00:42:32.504 --> 00:42:35.546
Main square is that way.
Just follow other people.

448
00:42:35.629 --> 00:42:36.880
I'm coming with you.

449
00:42:38.046 --> 00:42:42.546
I heard you on the phone earlier.
About pulling you two out.

450
00:42:44.546 --> 00:42:46.755
I know the others will be quarantined.

451
00:42:48.922 --> 00:42:50.088
It's not true. Su-an.

452
00:42:50.172 --> 00:42:51.838
- We're just...
- I'll tell the others.

453
00:42:51.922 --> 00:42:55.547
- You don't have to.
- Of course I do!

454
00:42:55.630 --> 00:42:58.005
Forget them!
Everyone is for themselves!

455
00:42:59.672 --> 00:43:03.297
You only care about yourself.

456
00:43:05.797 --> 00:43:09.464
That's why Mommy left.

457
00:43:28.464 --> 00:43:29.298
Sweetie.

458
00:43:33.631 --> 00:43:36.006
Here! Over here!

459
00:43:36.090 --> 00:43:38.006
Please help!

460
00:43:38.090 --> 00:43:41.548
- Sweetie. stay right here.
- Please help!

461
00:44:00.424 --> 00:44:02.215
Damn it. What's happening? Hold on!

462
00:44:04.132 --> 00:44:05.215
Hold on!

463
00:44:16.757 --> 00:44:18.466
Go back up! Go!

464
00:44:20.341 --> 00:44:21.424
Help!

465
00:44:21.507 --> 00:44:22.508
- What the...
- Hurry!

466
00:44:36.508 --> 00:44:37.841
- Lt. Min!
<i>- Mr. Seo!</i>

467
00:44:37.925 --> 00:44:38.841
I'm in Daejeon.

468
00:44:38.925 --> 00:44:41.383
<i>My men over there. I can't contact them!</i>

469
00:44:41.466 --> 00:44:42.341
What?

470
00:44:42.841 --> 00:44:44.091
<i>Hello?</i>

471
00:44:44.175 --> 00:44:45.258
Help me.

472
00:44:48.092 --> 00:44:49.008
Please...

473
00:45:03.217 --> 00:45:04.842
Su-an!

474
00:45:20.134 --> 00:45:21.134
Come on. hurry!

475
00:45:26.634 --> 00:45:29.843
- Come on! Hurry!
- Hurry!

476
00:45:41.551 --> 00:45:43.426
Hurry up! Quick!

477
00:45:44.343 --> 00:45:45.218
Block it!

478
00:46:03.635 --> 00:46:04.677
Run! Come on!

479
00:46:10.011 --> 00:46:11.302
Asshole! Come on!

480
00:46:19.636 --> 00:46:20.803
Faster!

481
00:46:23.386 --> 00:46:24.469
Hold them off!

482
00:46:58.012 --> 00:47:02.095
- Over here! Run!
- This way! Hurry!

483
00:47:02.179 --> 00:47:03.554
- Come on!
- Here!

484
00:47:04.929 --> 00:47:07.012
- Hurry!
- Here!

485
00:47:07.096 --> 00:47:09.012
- This way!
- Hurry!

486
00:47:09.096 --> 00:47:10.721
Come on!

487
00:47:10.804 --> 00:47:11.887
- Hurry!
- This way!

488
00:47:11.971 --> 00:47:16.429
- Why aren't we leaving yet?
- There are still more people!

489
00:47:16.512 --> 00:47:18.013
- Hurry up!
- Here!

490
00:47:18.096 --> 00:47:20.304
- Hurry!
- Come this way!

491
00:47:20.388 --> 00:47:22.971
- Hurry!
- Hurry!

492
00:47:23.054 --> 00:47:24.513
- Faster! Here!
- This way!

493
00:47:38.055 --> 00:47:41.347
Ma'am! Please get up!

494
00:47:49.930 --> 00:47:52.305
- No. stop!
- No!

495
00:47:52.388 --> 00:47:54.847
- My sister!
- Hurry!

496
00:48:00.930 --> 00:48:03.305
- Hop on!
- Hurry!

497
00:48:23.306 --> 00:48:24.139
Me too!

498
00:48:24.931 --> 00:48:29.015
Let me in! Please!

499
00:48:46.723 --> 00:48:49.265
How much longer? We have to leave!

500
00:48:49.348 --> 00:48:51.515
- No! My friends aren't here yet!
- Hey!

501
00:48:52.515 --> 00:48:54.515
Those on board must survive!

502
00:48:55.015 --> 00:48:57.099
Aren't I right?

503
00:49:02.849 --> 00:49:07.266
Conductor. please depart.

504
00:49:27.558 --> 00:49:29.058
Run! Let's go!

505
00:49:45.142 --> 00:49:47.683
Look. the train! Run faster!

506
00:50:07.351 --> 00:50:08.601
Snap out of it. idiot!

507
00:50:37.977 --> 00:50:38.810
Watch out!

508
00:51:00.727 --> 00:51:05.227
Control. Train 101 could not dock
at Daejeon due to an outbreak.

509
00:51:05.311 --> 00:51:08.394
Advise which station
is available to dock. over.

510
00:51:08.477 --> 00:51:13.686
<i>Train 101. Due to unstable communications.
it is difficult to advise.</i>

511
00:51:13.769 --> 00:51:18.811
Control. Is Train 101 clear
to reach Busan? Over.

512
00:51:21.769 --> 00:51:26.145
<i>Train 101. we'll clear
your route to Busan. Control center. out.</i>

513
00:51:27.645 --> 00:51:30.186
Advise when you make contact with Busan.

514
00:51:31.186 --> 00:51:32.353
Train 101. out.

515
00:52:47.980 --> 00:52:50.689
<i>Attention. everyone.</i>

516
00:52:50.772 --> 00:52:56.147
<i>For the safety of those on board.
we won't be making any stops.</i>

517
00:52:56.230 --> 00:52:58.272
<i>and will head straight for Busan.</i>

518
00:52:59.606 --> 00:53:03.522
- Conductor. can you hear me?
<i>- Go ahead.</i>

519
00:53:04.106 --> 00:53:05.814
Were you able to contact Busan?

520
00:53:05.897 --> 00:53:09.189
<i>No. the communication is erratic.</i>

521
00:53:09.273 --> 00:53:12.148
Full speed. no matter what!

522
00:53:12.856 --> 00:53:14.773
Or we won't get in. understand?

523
00:53:22.523 --> 00:53:24.315
Yeong-guk. where are you?

524
00:53:24.940 --> 00:53:25.773
Damn it.

525
00:53:26.898 --> 00:53:29.856
I thought you were dead!

526
00:53:29.940 --> 00:53:31.315
I'm sorry.

527
00:53:33.773 --> 00:53:37.898
No one else made it. I'm sorry.

528
00:53:47.982 --> 00:53:49.274
<i>The number you have dialed...</i>

529
00:53:49.357 --> 00:53:51.607
- Baby?
<i>- Mister!</i>

530
00:53:52.649 --> 00:53:55.232
Why are you answering? Where are you?

531
00:53:55.315 --> 00:54:00.524
<i>- We're in the train washroom!</i>
- Washroom? Which car?

532
00:54:00.607 --> 00:54:03.191
<i>Well. it's...</i>

533
00:54:03.274 --> 00:54:04.607
<i>Car 13!</i>

534
00:54:04.691 --> 00:54:06.691
<i>- Get your ass over here right now!</i>
- Baby!

535
00:54:10.358 --> 00:54:12.441
Was that my kid? Is she okay?

536
00:54:13.066 --> 00:54:14.608
They're in the washroom in Car 13.

537
00:54:29.858 --> 00:54:30.816
Gonna pass through?

538
00:54:33.150 --> 00:54:37.275
Let's say you make it and rescue them.
How will you come back?

539
00:54:41.733 --> 00:54:42.900
In Car 15.

540
00:54:44.775 --> 00:54:46.109
people are gathered there.

541
00:55:11.359 --> 00:55:13.359
Only four cars away.

542
00:55:15.359 --> 00:55:16.359
I'll lead.

543
00:55:18.151 --> 00:55:19.068
You in the middle.

544
00:55:20.818 --> 00:55:21.818
And you in the back.

545
00:55:25.318 --> 00:55:27.276
Block anyone attacking from the rear.

546
00:55:39.360 --> 00:55:41.444
I heard you're a fund manager.

547
00:55:44.610 --> 00:55:49.360
Then you're an expert
at leaving useless people behind.

548
00:55:56.361 --> 00:55:57.736
Wait till we exit the tunnel.

549
00:56:12.944 --> 00:56:13.778
Let's go.

550
00:57:25.405 --> 00:57:26.988
Come on!

551
00:57:28.947 --> 00:57:29.905
Let's go!

552
00:57:46.864 --> 00:57:47.697
Out of the way.

553
00:59:23.158 --> 00:59:24.158
Run!

554
00:59:31.283 --> 00:59:32.158
Move over.

555
00:59:36.284 --> 00:59:40.034
They stopped
once we entered the tunnel. right?

556
00:59:40.909 --> 00:59:44.534
- Probably because it got dark.
- Yeah. I think so too.

557
00:59:47.284 --> 00:59:48.909
There are even more here.

558
00:59:50.576 --> 00:59:51.617
What do we do now?

559
00:59:53.159 --> 00:59:54.492
We have no choice.

560
00:59:55.367 --> 00:59:56.201
Let's go.

561
01:00:00.326 --> 01:00:01.951
- What?
- Give me your phone.

562
01:01:35.204 --> 01:01:36.037
Are you okay?

563
01:02:06.704 --> 01:02:08.080
Get that out of my face.

564
01:02:10.913 --> 01:02:11.913
Yo. douche.

565
01:02:13.246 --> 01:02:17.080
Felt good to see your kid. thanks to me?

566
01:02:17.163 --> 01:02:19.622
Are you grateful or what?

567
01:02:19.705 --> 01:02:21.955
Why is your ringtone so tacky?

568
01:02:23.288 --> 01:02:25.205
What's wrong with it?

569
01:02:26.872 --> 01:02:29.247
How do I change it?

570
01:02:30.330 --> 01:02:34.539
Am I funny? You little rat.

571
01:02:35.622 --> 01:02:37.997
- How tall are you?
- I'm 181 cm.

572
01:02:38.830 --> 01:02:41.830
Ten kilometers away.
at 300 kilometers an hour...

573
01:02:41.914 --> 01:02:42.747
What?

574
01:02:46.122 --> 01:02:47.039
Two minutes.

575
01:02:47.122 --> 01:02:49.372
The upcoming tunnel
will give us two minutes.

576
01:02:49.456 --> 01:02:52.289
- Can we do it?
- We gotta.

577
01:02:52.914 --> 01:02:57.123
If we miss this one.
there's another in three kilometers.

578
01:02:57.206 --> 01:03:01.289
I bet you never get to play
with your daughter.

579
01:03:03.206 --> 01:03:04.873
When she gets older.

580
01:03:06.290 --> 01:03:09.165
she'll understand why you work so hard.

581
01:03:11.415 --> 01:03:14.540
Dads get all the bad rap and no praise.

582
01:03:15.331 --> 01:03:17.248
But it's all about sacrifice. right?

583
01:03:21.040 --> 01:03:24.165
What's with the look? Did I sound cool?

584
01:03:24.748 --> 01:03:25.582
Yeah?

585
01:03:33.040 --> 01:03:34.540
PEOPLE RESCUED. HEADING OVER NOW

586
01:03:36.249 --> 01:03:39.957
- My friend's coming here!
- What? What did you say?

587
01:03:40.040 --> 01:03:43.624
My friend from another car is coming over.

588
01:03:43.707 --> 01:03:45.874
- Who's coming?
- My friend.

589
01:03:45.957 --> 01:03:47.624
He was in Car 9.

590
01:03:47.707 --> 01:03:49.666
He rescued some people.
and they're headed here.

591
01:03:49.749 --> 01:03:50.666
Rescued?

592
01:03:52.666 --> 01:03:57.208
From there to here.
passing through those monsters?

593
01:03:58.374 --> 01:03:59.624
Without any injuries?

594
01:04:01.333 --> 01:04:02.833
You sure they're not infected?

595
01:04:04.166 --> 01:04:07.083
Are you damn sure?

596
01:04:08.375 --> 01:04:10.125
What do you mean?

597
01:04:10.208 --> 01:04:12.958
Hey. Look at these people.

598
01:04:13.583 --> 01:04:15.291
At this moment.

599
01:04:15.375 --> 01:04:18.083
there are so many people here
who don't know

600
01:04:18.167 --> 01:04:20.000
what happened to their families.

601
01:04:20.958 --> 01:04:25.500
We don't even know
if your damn friends are infected!

602
01:04:26.083 --> 01:04:28.500
And you want to let them in here?

603
01:04:33.000 --> 01:04:34.167
I don't believe this.

604
01:04:44.251 --> 01:04:45.459
Sir.

605
01:04:48.001 --> 01:04:50.251
please say something.

606
01:04:51.084 --> 01:04:52.876
They'll be here soon.

607
01:04:55.251 --> 01:04:56.543
Sir!

608
01:04:57.626 --> 01:04:58.626
Sir.

609
01:08:44.424 --> 01:08:45.799
Get over here!

610
01:08:54.508 --> 01:08:55.466
One.

611
01:08:58.175 --> 01:08:59.175
Two.

612
01:09:05.591 --> 01:09:06.550
Run!

613
01:09:10.092 --> 01:09:11.008
Come on!

614
01:09:17.217 --> 01:09:18.092
Hey!

615
01:09:20.133 --> 01:09:22.217
Jin-hui!

616
01:09:24.800 --> 01:09:26.342
Hurry the hell up!

617
01:09:36.509 --> 01:09:40.551
Open up! Hey. open this door!

618
01:09:42.342 --> 01:09:46.259
- Open the door!
- Open this door!

619
01:09:47.134 --> 01:09:48.218
Open this door!

620
01:09:48.801 --> 01:09:49.676
Jin-hui!

621
01:09:59.135 --> 01:10:00.010
Open the door!

622
01:10:00.593 --> 01:10:04.093
- Open up!
- Jin-hui!

623
01:10:14.343 --> 01:10:15.802
Open it now!

624
01:10:16.302 --> 01:10:19.135
It won't budge! I can't open it!

625
01:10:19.218 --> 01:10:20.844
Smash it!

626
01:10:21.427 --> 01:10:22.344
Stand back.

627
01:10:29.177 --> 01:10:30.385
Hurry up!

628
01:10:33.219 --> 01:10:35.511
Damn it.

629
01:11:00.345 --> 01:11:01.928
You stupid idiots!

630
01:11:14.887 --> 01:11:16.595
Damn it! Come on!

631
01:11:28.387 --> 01:11:29.637
In-gil.

632
01:11:34.471 --> 01:11:35.804
Yeong-guk!

633
01:11:38.137 --> 01:11:39.637
Stand back!

634
01:11:40.429 --> 01:11:41.596
Yeong-guk!

635
01:12:16.638 --> 01:12:17.680
Stay away!

636
01:12:24.597 --> 01:12:28.430
Stay back. baby. Please go!

637
01:12:34.847 --> 01:12:36.389
Buddy. hey!

638
01:12:37.056 --> 01:12:39.889
Take her and leave.

639
01:12:41.014 --> 01:12:42.598
You have to go.

640
01:12:43.848 --> 01:12:45.598
I said go. douche!

641
01:12:47.389 --> 01:12:49.264
I'm getting tired. Please go.

642
01:12:53.306 --> 01:12:57.098
Take care of her. okay?

643
01:12:57.598 --> 01:13:01.515
I'll hold them off. Just go!

644
01:13:11.932 --> 01:13:13.807
I'm sorry.

645
01:13:24.599 --> 01:13:26.432
We have to go. Let's go!

646
01:13:28.557 --> 01:13:29.766
Yun Seo-yeon!

647
01:13:32.307 --> 01:13:34.016
That's our baby's name!

648
01:13:35.266 --> 01:13:36.099
Got it?

649
01:15:36.603 --> 01:15:37.936
Why did you do it?

650
01:15:40.144 --> 01:15:41.519
You bastard!

651
01:15:43.561 --> 01:15:44.978
We could've saved them!

652
01:15:47.436 --> 01:15:48.311
Why?

653
01:15:49.895 --> 01:15:51.395
He's infected!

654
01:15:52.770 --> 01:15:54.686
He's one of them!

655
01:15:55.353 --> 01:15:56.853
This guy is infected!

656
01:15:56.936 --> 01:15:59.020
His eyes! Look at his eyes!

657
01:15:59.103 --> 01:16:01.812
He'll become one of them!

658
01:16:01.895 --> 01:16:03.312
Do you all want to die?

659
01:16:03.395 --> 01:16:04.687
We must throw them out!

660
01:16:09.562 --> 01:16:10.645
Hey!

661
01:16:15.854 --> 01:16:18.395
Those of you who just arrived.

662
01:16:19.645 --> 01:16:22.312
I don't think you can stay with us.

663
01:16:24.229 --> 01:16:25.854
Please move to the vestibule.

664
01:16:41.063 --> 01:16:41.979
Just go!

665
01:16:45.313 --> 01:16:47.063
- Get out!
- Hurry up and leave!

666
01:16:47.146 --> 01:16:48.480
Leave now!

667
01:16:54.771 --> 01:16:55.771
Get out now!

668
01:16:57.688 --> 01:16:58.855
Hurry up!

669
01:17:00.063 --> 01:17:01.063
Move!

670
01:17:03.647 --> 01:17:07.022
- Go!
- Leave us!

671
01:17:07.105 --> 01:17:08.938
- Get the hell out!
- Hurry!

672
01:17:10.897 --> 01:17:12.189
Out now!

673
01:17:14.022 --> 01:17:16.064
- Hurry!
- Get out now!

674
01:17:16.147 --> 01:17:18.564
- Come on!
- Hurry!

675
01:17:18.647 --> 01:17:21.564
It'll be safer for you to stay here.

676
01:17:21.647 --> 01:17:24.689
No. This place is scarier.

677
01:17:26.064 --> 01:17:27.314
I'm coming with you.

678
01:17:27.397 --> 01:17:28.272
But...

679
01:17:28.356 --> 01:17:29.814
Get the hell out!

680
01:17:30.356 --> 01:17:32.439
What are you waiting for?

681
01:17:32.981 --> 01:17:34.189
Okay. let's go.

682
01:17:36.939 --> 01:17:39.439
Get out. the rest of you!

683
01:17:39.939 --> 01:17:41.356
Get out!

684
01:17:41.439 --> 01:17:43.356
Get out of here!

685
01:18:01.315 --> 01:18:02.232
Let's go.

686
01:18:38.858 --> 01:18:41.233
- Tie it faster!
- Tie it there. too!

687
01:18:41.316 --> 01:18:43.275
- Hurry!
- More ties! Neckties!

688
01:18:43.358 --> 01:18:45.400
Shut up! I'm working on it!

689
01:19:01.733 --> 01:19:05.108
You idiot. Good riddance.

690
01:19:06.525 --> 01:19:10.234
Always helping others instead of yourself.

691
01:19:14.859 --> 01:19:16.900
Why did you lead such a difficult life

692
01:19:18.359 --> 01:19:20.734
if you were going to end up like this?

693
01:19:22.067 --> 01:19:23.401
So stupid.

694
01:19:30.651 --> 01:19:32.109
Shut up! Be quiet!

695
01:19:33.359 --> 01:19:34.609
Stay in your seat!

696
01:19:35.859 --> 01:19:38.151
What a load of shit.

697
01:19:43.068 --> 01:19:45.193
Finish up and do the other side too.

698
01:19:56.110 --> 01:19:59.985
Thank you for everything.

699
01:20:01.443 --> 01:20:04.318
That bitch. Stop her!

700
01:20:58.403 --> 01:21:01.195
Control! This is Busan-bound Train 101!

701
01:21:01.278 --> 01:21:03.195
Requesting current status report. over!

702
01:21:04.487 --> 01:21:07.112
Control? Control!

703
01:22:33.948 --> 01:22:35.573
It's your birthday today.

704
01:22:40.198 --> 01:22:41.281
Don't worry.

705
01:22:42.073 --> 01:22:43.948
I'll take you to Mom. no matter what.

706
01:22:48.073 --> 01:22:49.907
Aren't you scared?

707
01:22:55.948 --> 01:22:56.990
Of course I am.

708
01:22:59.240 --> 01:23:00.407
I'm scared too.

709
01:23:05.157 --> 01:23:07.282
I was so scared earlier.

710
01:23:07.990 --> 01:23:10.990
I thought I'd never see you again.

711
01:23:13.199 --> 01:23:17.907
I practiced that song just for you.

712
01:23:22.366 --> 01:23:24.199
That's why I couldn't finish.

713
01:23:26.908 --> 01:23:28.533
Because you weren't there.

714
01:23:36.283 --> 01:23:38.491
Will you stay with me from now on?

715
01:23:52.783 --> 01:23:56.617
NA-YEONG

716
01:24:06.409 --> 01:24:11.951
<i>The person you're calling
is not available.</i>

717
01:24:21.284 --> 01:24:25.576
ANALYST KIM

718
01:24:27.534 --> 01:24:28.534
Yes. Kim.

719
01:24:30.409 --> 01:24:32.118
<i>Have you arrived at Busan yet?</i>

720
01:24:32.201 --> 01:24:34.993
Not yet. where are you?
Are you okay there?

721
01:24:36.743 --> 01:24:39.451
<i>I heard they succeeded
in defending Busan at an early stage.</i>

722
01:24:39.535 --> 01:24:42.160
What? You sure?

723
01:24:42.743 --> 01:24:44.285
Where did you get that info?

724
01:24:45.160 --> 01:24:49.327
<i>Sir. I heard
that all of this started at YS Biotech.</i>

725
01:24:51.910 --> 01:24:56.035
<i>The very same company
we saved with our scheme!</i>

726
01:25:00.452 --> 01:25:01.369
<i>Sir.</i>

727
01:25:02.202 --> 01:25:05.202
<i>This has nothing to do with us. right?</i>

728
01:25:06.410 --> 01:25:09.285
<i>We only do what we are told to.</i>

729
01:25:09.369 --> 01:25:13.036
<i>This is not my fault. right?</i>

730
01:25:16.369 --> 01:25:17.327
Kim.

731
01:25:18.619 --> 01:25:19.952
it's not your fault.

732
01:25:23.953 --> 01:25:25.036
<i>Thank you.</i>

733
01:25:27.328 --> 01:25:28.244
Kim...

734
01:26:50.663 --> 01:26:57.664
{\an8}DONGDAEGU STATION

735
01:27:13.372 --> 01:27:15.122
Attention. please.

736
01:27:15.206 --> 01:27:19.623
<i>Due to a blockage on our track.</i>

737
01:27:19.706 --> 01:27:22.164
<i>we have stopped at Dongdaegu Station.</i>

738
01:27:22.248 --> 01:27:25.998
<i>We should either wait for the rescue team.</i>

739
01:27:26.081 --> 01:27:30.915
<i>or we'll have to reach
Busan in another train.</i>

740
01:27:31.456 --> 01:27:33.706
<i>As soon as I end this announcement.</i>

741
01:27:33.790 --> 01:27:39.290
<i>I will find a working train
and put it on the leftmost track.</i>

742
01:27:39.373 --> 01:27:42.832
- What's he saying?
<i>- I repeat. leftmost track.</i>

743
01:27:42.915 --> 01:27:47.873
If you're alive. please transfer safely.

744
01:27:49.873 --> 01:27:50.998
Godspeed.

745
01:28:56.875 --> 01:28:58.875
Do you think they'll send a rescue team?

746
01:29:01.417 --> 01:29:03.459
I heard that Busan is safe.

747
01:29:06.001 --> 01:29:07.459
We have to move now.

748
01:29:31.168 --> 01:29:32.001
Here.

749
01:30:02.377 --> 01:30:03.461
What the...

750
01:30:52.462 --> 01:30:53.629
Is the coast clear?

751
01:30:56.795 --> 01:30:57.629
Yeah.

752
01:31:00.754 --> 01:31:01.796
You go first.

753
01:31:26.380 --> 01:31:28.130
We have to find a way across.

754
01:31:30.755 --> 01:31:31.588
Let's go.

755
01:31:33.713 --> 01:31:34.546
Let's go.

756
01:31:51.922 --> 01:31:53.130
What in the...

757
01:32:05.714 --> 01:32:06.589
Over here!

758
01:32:44.007 --> 01:32:46.132
- No.
- Oh no.

759
01:32:47.174 --> 01:32:50.007
- What now?
- Hey!

760
01:32:50.799 --> 01:32:52.924
We have to move. come on!

761
01:33:00.966 --> 01:33:02.466
Jin-hui. hurry!

762
01:33:18.924 --> 01:33:19.883
Stand back.

763
01:33:33.216 --> 01:33:34.175
Jin-hui!

764
01:33:48.509 --> 01:33:49.675
Jin-hui!

765
01:33:50.509 --> 01:33:51.384
Jin-hui.

766
01:34:01.342 --> 01:34:02.759
This can't be.

767
01:34:08.884 --> 01:34:09.926
I'm sorry.

768
01:34:32.802 --> 01:34:38.218
Daddy!

769
01:34:38.302 --> 01:34:42.968
Daddy! Wake up!

770
01:34:43.552 --> 01:34:47.802
Daddy!

771
01:34:49.094 --> 01:34:50.844
Daddy!

772
01:35:03.177 --> 01:35:04.844
What's going on?

773
01:35:08.761 --> 01:35:10.469
Come on. faster!

774
01:35:11.594 --> 01:35:12.636
Hurry!

775
01:35:18.344 --> 01:35:19.678
Damn it!

776
01:35:21.886 --> 01:35:23.886
Hurry!

777
01:35:36.137 --> 01:35:37.428
Help.

778
01:36:20.680 --> 01:36:21.846
Sweetie. come here!

779
01:36:26.805 --> 01:36:28.555
Su-an.

780
01:36:45.055 --> 01:36:45.889
Mister!

781
01:37:04.598 --> 01:37:05.431
Sweetie!

782
01:37:05.514 --> 01:37:07.473
Su-an. come here!

783
01:37:07.973 --> 01:37:09.014
Mister.

784
01:37:09.098 --> 01:37:11.514
Go! Hurry!

785
01:37:11.598 --> 01:37:12.556
Come on!

786
01:37:13.139 --> 01:37:13.973
Hurry!

787
01:37:15.348 --> 01:37:16.181
Quick!

788
01:37:36.432 --> 01:37:37.473
Let's go!

789
01:39:00.726 --> 01:39:02.018
Hurry!

790
01:39:05.601 --> 01:39:06.476
Daddy!

791
01:41:28.272 --> 01:41:29.272
Mister.

792
01:41:31.313 --> 01:41:32.397
I'm scared.

793
01:41:35.480 --> 01:41:37.564
Take me home.

794
01:41:37.647 --> 01:41:42.772
My mom is waiting for me.

795
01:41:46.481 --> 01:41:48.106
My address is

796
01:41:48.772 --> 01:41:52.856
